            "body": "https://github.com/neovim/neovim/blob/d12dd07c7af94fadd20874ccc22eaa55ac40c41f/src/nvim/os/fs.c#L299-L301\n\nHere, we treat `bash.exe` as a Unix shell, so `exepath` returns a path without the file extension, which causes `spawn` to fail.\n\nhttps://github.com/neovim/neovim/blob/d12dd07c7af94fadd20874ccc22eaa55ac40c41f/src/nvim/os/fs.c#L333-L335\n\nhttps://github.com/neovim/neovim/blob/df5d559878567c02e3ceaa2e2d45417111486fcb/runtime/lua/vim/_core/system.lua#L319-L326\n\n",
            "created_at": "2026-05-07T10:42:15Z",
            "html_url": "https://github.com/neovim/neovim/issues/39298#issuecomment-4396396962",
            "id": 4396396962,
            "issue_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/neovim/neovim/issues/39298",
